{"productOptionsHtml":"<div class=\"space-y-4 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-800\">\n<p class=\"text-neutral-600\">Use this section for <strong class=\"text-neutral-900\">ordering rules</strong>: style number, price band, minimums, and stated production time from the supplier catalog. Final invoice may reflect decoration, proofs, rush, or freight.</p>\n<table class=\"w-full border-collapse text-left text-[13px]\">\n<thead><tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-200 text-[11px] uppercase tracking-wide text-neutral-500\"><th class=\"py-2 pr-3 font-medium\">Field</th><th class=\"py-2 font-medium\">Value</th></tr></thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-500 align-top\">Style #</td><td class=\"py-2 font-mono text-neutral-900\">SE-WH-34</td></tr>\n<tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-500 align-top\">List price range</td><td class=\"py-2\">$1.22 – $4.27 USD</td></tr>\n<tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-500 align-top\">Minimum quantity</td><td class=\"py-2\">50</td></tr>\n<tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-500 align-top\">Stated production time</td><td class=\"py-2\">16 days</td></tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h4 class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-neutral-700 mt-5 mb-2\">Quantity pricing (USD)</h4>\n<p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600 mb-2\">Price per unit at each order-quantity break (from the live product page).</p>\n<table class=\"w-full border-collapse text-left text-[13px]\">\n<thead><tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-200 text-[11px] uppercase tracking-wide text-neutral-500\"><th class=\"py-2 pr-3 font-medium\">Quantity</th><th class=\"py-2 font-medium\">Price (each)</th></tr></thead>\n<tbody><tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-800 tabular-nums\">50</td><td class=\"py-2 tabular-nums\">$4.27 each</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-800 tabular-nums\">100</td><td class=\"py-2 tabular-nums\">$2.70 each</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-800 tabular-nums\">200</td><td class=\"py-2 tabular-nums\">$2.00 each</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-800 tabular-nums\">300</td><td class=\"py-2 tabular-nums\">$1.79 each</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-800 tabular-nums\">500</td><td class=\"py-2 tabular-nums\">$1.59 each</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-800 tabular-nums\">1000</td><td class=\"py-2 tabular-nums\">$1.46 each</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-800 tabular-nums\">2500</td><td class=\"py-2 tabular-nums\">$1.34 each</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-800 tabular-nums\">5000</td><td class=\"py-2 tabular-nums\">$1.26 each</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-800 tabular-nums\">10000</td><td class=\"py-2 tabular-nums\">$1.22 each</td></tr></tbody>\n</table>\n<h4 class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-neutral-700 mt-5 mb-2\">Catalog highlights</h4><ul class=\"list-disc pl-5 space-y-1 text-[13px] leading-snug\"><li>High quality finish and bright vibrant colors</li><li>Butterfly or Rubber Clutch Included</li><li>Individually Polybagged</li><li>Custom Shape and Size</li><li>PMS color matching up to 4 colors</li></ul>\n<div class=\"not-prose mt-5\">\n<h4 class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-neutral-700 mb-2\">Patch options (supplier)</h4>\n<p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600 mb-3\">Options and add-ons from the live Distributor Central product page for this SKU. Pricing may change; confirm on your quote.</p>\n<div class=\"overflow-hidden rounded-lg border border-neutral-200 bg-neutral-50/30\">\n<details class=\"group border-b border-neutral-200 last:border-b-0 open:bg-neutral-50/50\">\n<summary class=\"cursor-pointer list-none py-3 pl-1 pr-2 text-[13px] font-semibold text-neutral-900 outline-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden\">\n<span class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-3\">\n<span>Backing Options - Pins</span>\n<span class=\"mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-[10px] font-normal text-neutral-400 transition group-open:rotate-180\" aria-hidden=\"true\">▼</span>\n</span>\n</summary>\n<div class=\"border-t border-neutral-100 bg-white px-1 pb-3 pt-2\"><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/1/8/18D46ECD4119565B2EF2793D8AB625BD.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Magnet Backing</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">Quote Upon Request</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] font-medium text-neutral-800\">$0.80 each</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/7/F/7F3C3E32BEC5DB04394632F4CED43B1F.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Butterfly Clutch</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">This back is included in the cost of the pin.</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/5/2/5273F2A1ABDB2A32D79C98254A0594C6.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Rubber Clutch</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">This back is included in the cost of the pin.</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/E/0/E0B1A958923A80708123C49E3FBB2523.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Safety Pin Backing</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] font-medium text-neutral-800\">$0.16 each</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/2/7/2704490835FCCE68A77CB7326229FEF9.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Tie Tack Backing</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] font-medium text-neutral-800\">$0.38 each</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/1/0/10917CB530EF6C0E430C1A6C85FE6459.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Additional Butterfly Clutch</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">This option is for if your pin requires a second butterfly clutch for stability or if you decide to add a second clutch.</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] font-medium text-neutral-800\">$0.10 each</p></div></div>\n</details>\n<details class=\"group border-b border-neutral-200 last:border-b-0 open:bg-neutral-50/50\">\n<summary class=\"cursor-pointer list-none py-3 pl-1 pr-2 text-[13px] font-semibold text-neutral-900 outline-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden\">\n<span class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-3\">\n<span>Additional Options - Pins</span>\n<span class=\"mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-[10px] font-normal text-neutral-400 transition group-open:rotate-180\" aria-hidden=\"true\">▼</span>\n</span>\n</summary>\n<div class=\"border-t border-neutral-100 bg-white px-1 pb-3 pt-2\"><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/1/7/17184B3C279B8DF75DBFDFE2B2DAF81F.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Over 4 Colors - Pins</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">This option is if you require more than 4 soft enamel colors in the pin. Only up to 4 colors are included in the cost of the pin.\n\nPlease note that costs are per additional color/per pin.</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] font-medium text-neutral-800\">$0.08 each</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/7/B/7B9717081C33D10891BC8BB14C76AF52.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">3D Images SE - Pins</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">3D Images SE- Pins</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">This option allows for a 3D pin with raised portions that are sure to stand out.</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] font-medium text-neutral-800\">$125.00 each</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/7/8/78B53E275E18A3E363E61E51C6418E3B.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Cut Out - Pins</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">This option allows you to add a cut out area in a lapel pin\n\nPlease note that this cost is per location/per pin.</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] font-medium text-neutral-800\">$0.05 each · $20.00 each</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/B/3/B3D838DCAD37F6DBEC062C2140733BFA.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Sandblasting SE - Pins</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Sandblasting SE- Pins</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">This is a free sandblasting option.</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/B/6/B6A3317E532AC4D21826517B6BB1AB51.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Laser Engraving SE - Pins</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Laser Engraving SE- Pins</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">This is a laser engraving option.</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] font-medium text-neutral-800\">$0.24 each</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/C/9/C9861DED428D7276B89C75EC2FBF2682.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Dual Plating - Pins</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">This option allows you to have more than one type of metal on the pin, for instance, Gold and Nickel.  \n\nPlease note that costs may vary depending on the amount of each metal present on the coin.\n\nCosts are available upon quote request.</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/5/1/516F691ED5AE38D3C5C04773C2AB13BA.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Silk Screen Printing - Pins</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">This option allows you to add Silk Screened text to the pin. \n\nPlease note that depending on the placement of the silk screened text an epoxy dome may be required. \n\nCost is per color/per pin.</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] font-medium text-neutral-800\">$0.08 each · $50.00 each</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/9/E/9EC21DE23FDDB4F644A3184CC47D9A67.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Epoxy Dome - Pins</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">This option allows you to add an epoxy dome to the pin.</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] font-medium text-neutral-800\">$0.14 each</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/3/6/366538FB3FDA4FDAA530DD4EA19E6DF3.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Glitter Fill - Pins</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">This option allows you to add a Glitter Fill to a soft enamel color in the pin.</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] font-medium text-neutral-800\">$0.40 each</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/5/E/5ED544A5393846F22C446DA3E5167B81.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Simulated Gems - Pins</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">This option allows you to add a simulated gem to the pin. Please note that costs are per gem/per pin.</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] font-medium text-neutral-800\">$0.20 each · $20.00 each</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/9/D/9DC6F2C49E596EC4BC0FACDD4C162ADB.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Rocker - Pins</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">This option allows you to add a rocker to the pin. \n\nCost is available upon quote request.</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/1/3/13D319AB152367DC568D351DFE1ED03F.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Glow in the Dark - Pins</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">This option allows you to add Glow in the Dark areas to the pin. \n\nCosts are available upon quote request.</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] font-medium text-neutral-800\">$0.30 each</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/4/3/43E013883955855C447E2EC51D3EE48D.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">LED Light - Pins</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">This option allows you to add an LED light to the pin. \n\nCost is available upon quote request.</p></div></div>\n</details>\n<details class=\"group border-b border-neutral-200 last:border-b-0 open:bg-neutral-50/50\">\n<summary class=\"cursor-pointer list-none py-3 pl-1 pr-2 text-[13px] font-semibold text-neutral-900 outline-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden\">\n<span class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-3\">\n<span>Plating Options - SE</span>\n<span class=\"mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-[10px] font-normal text-neutral-400 transition group-open:rotate-180\" aria-hidden=\"true\">▼</span>\n</span>\n</summary>\n<div class=\"border-t border-neutral-100 bg-white px-1 pb-3 pt-2\"><p class=\"mb-3 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">These are the plating options for pins. Plating is the metal shown on the pin itself.</p><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/4/1/41438845D16F2E6EB4C33924B25FB32A.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Black Nickel Plating - SE</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">This plating choice is an additional charge of 25% per pin. There is no set amount.</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/6/C/6C54A5F88DE92B60281626EAC38D45C7.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Gold Plating</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">This plating choice is free.</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/1/C/1C