180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Antique Silver Plating - Pins</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">Antique Plating run charges for lapel pins to $0.50(R) Run charge</p></div></div>\n</details>\n<details class=\"group border-b border-neutral-200 last:border-b-0 open:bg-neutral-50/50\">\n<summary class=\"cursor-pointer list-none py-3 pl-1 pr-2 text-[13px] font-semibold text-neutral-900 outline-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden\">\n<span class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-3\">\n<span>Packaging Options - Pins</span>\n<span class=\"mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-[10px] font-normal text-neutral-400 transition group-open:rotate-180\" aria-hidden=\"true\">▼</span>\n</span>\n</summary>\n<div class=\"border-t border-neutral-100 bg-white px-1 pb-3 pt-2\"><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/E/9/E943388BE93FC3A9356DF9C933AD25CD.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Custom Backing Card- Pins</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Packaging - Pins</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">quote upon request\n\nCustomizable up to 3&quot; x 4&quot; Full color print</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/7/0/70B3FE445D9C918031BA0C7E4C3D359B.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Cardboard Box- Pins</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Packaging - Pins</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">quote upon request</p></div><div class=\"border-b bor